  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dinosis Survival is a third person shooter with dinosaurs based on a mysterious story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a player, we control a man named Tom Burt. He woke up in the jungle full of dinosaurs after his plane crashed. Is he the only one that survived the crash? What is this place?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most important gameplay elements are hunting and sneaking. Dinosaurs can see you, can smell you, can attack you or run away when hurt. You will find many weapons, puzzles, and clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunger is a very important issue in the game. You can hunt or grab some dinosaur’s eggs to eat and restore energy. To cook dinosaur meat, you must make a fire camp in safe place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an Indie production made by one single person, but it has been polished and designed with care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dinosis Survival is a third person shooter with dinosaurs based on a mysterious story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a player, we control a man named Tom Burt. He woke up in the jungle full of dinosaurs after his plane crashed. Is he the only one that survived the crash? What is this place?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The most important gameplay elements are hunting and sneaking. Dinosaurs can see you, can smell you, can attack you or run away when hurt. You will find many weapons, puzzles, and clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunger is a very important issue in the game. You can hunt or grab some dinosaur’s eggs to eat and restore energy. To cook dinosaur meat, you must make a fire camp in safe place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an Indie production made by one single person, but it has been polished and designed with care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
